<paragraph blockId="3.[827,1444,1790,1843]" pageId="3" pageNumber="402">
<emphasis box="[827,957,1790,1811]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="402">Etymology:</emphasis>
The specific name is the Latin noun 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Guo &amp; Selden &amp; Ren" authorityYear="2022" box="[1400,1436,1791,1812]" class="Arachnida" family="Lagonomegopidae" genus="Scopomegops" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="3" pageNumber="402" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fax">
